headline: Wall Street Roundup: Market Reacts To Earnings
summary: Oracle's earnings showed mixed results, leading to an 11% drop. Broadcom's strong earnings overshadowed by warnings of margin pressures.

headline: Is United Airlines Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: United Airlines has fallen well behind the Nasdaq Composite over the past year, but analysts are doubling down with a striking level of conviction, projecting a sharp rebound and positioning the stock as one of the sector’s most compelling comeback stories.
